init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: At first you watch in horror, but eventually you find yourself rooting for the guy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are able to experience the emotions of when they were feeling the emotion.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: you find yourself once again watching yourself die.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is then that you are given a choice.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You get up and walk away.
